    "summary": "As Senior Manager at Deloitte Risk Advisory - Regulatory Risk & Compliance I'm responsible for our Compliance Risk Management services within FSI and the business development thereof. \n\nThis broad proposition covers everything with a connection to the optimization of Compliance risk management, including (re)design and assessing KYC/CDD | Compliance function (maturity) evaluation and (re)design | Systematic Integrity Risk Analysis (SIRA) evaluation and execution | Data-driven Compliance | Product risk assessments | Compliance (/KYC) gap-analyses and audits | Implementation of risk & control frameworks | Policy, guidance and process evaluation and design | Compliance benchmarking | Governance/thee lines of defense | and leveraging compliance expertise between industries. \n\nIn my role as senior manager I lead assignment teams on a daily bases within both the first line/business and second line/Compliance. Besides, I have fulfilled different MLRO and (international) Compliance officer roles within banking (large and midsize) and insurance sector.\n\nBetween 2012-2019 I have been involved in several large international financial crime projects based in Zurich, Edinburgh, Frankfurt and Copenhagen.\n\n<<if you are interested in the topics as mentioned above yourself or if you want to know more, please don't hesitate to drop me an email. I'm always looking for new talent to expand my team>>",
